{"result": {"history_size": 1, "folders": ["2018", "lecture11"], "nr": 1189, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "created": "2018-04-04T01:41:55Z", "bucket_order": 3, "no_answer_followup": 0, "change_log": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "data": "jfkffypyj6e5rv", "type": "create", "when": "2018-04-04T01:41:55Z"}, {"anon": "no", "uid": "j7f1tr6wJNH", "to": "jfkffypwx375ru", "type": "followup", "when": "2018-04-04T02:25:17Z"}, {"anon": "no", "uid": "j7f1tr6wJNH", "to": "jfkffypwx375ru", "type": "feedback", "when": "2018-04-04T08:47:43Z"}], "bucket_name": "Today", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "subject": "进程与线程的关系", "created": "2018-04-04T01:41:55Z", "content": "<p>问题&#xff1a;</p>\n<p><br />今天在群里&#xff0c;有个同学说&#xff0c;只有一个main函数的程序没有线程。<br />然后他也一直没说明白&#xff0c;一会儿说系统资源&#xff0c;一会儿说ucore不支持线程<br />我认为线程和进程一样&#xff0c;只是一个抽象&#xff0c;目前的系统中都是支持线程的&#xff0c;那肯定会有个主线程。<br />因为我很久没有看相关资料书了&#xff0c;记得之前看CSAPP时候有句话是说“每个进程创建的时候都会有个主线程&#xff0c;然后在某个时刻会创建一个对等线程”。所以应该在现代操作系统中。所有的进程都是有≥1个的线程吧。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>回答&#xff1a;<br />进程是指一个具有一定独立功能的程序在一个数据集合上的一次动态执行过程。线程是进程的一部分&#xff0c;描述指令流执行状态。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>11.6节幻灯片中第7页的图示直观地描述进程与线程的关系。线程只把原来的“进程”概念中的一部分内容“堆栈和寄存器&#xff08;包括当前指令指针&#xff09;”扩展到多份。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>所以&#xff0c;你的描述“所有的进程都是有≥1个的线程”是正确的。没有引入“线程”前的“进程”就是“单线程进程”。“只有一个main函数的程序没有线程”是错误的。“ucore不支持线程”也是错误的。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>这个问题是容易混淆的。如果对这个问题还有疑问&#xff0c;欢迎同学们继续回复本帖进行讨论。</p>"}], "type": "note", "tags": ["2018", "instructor-note", "lecture11"], "tag_good": [], "unique_views": 176, "children": [{"anon": "no", "folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": null}, "no_upvotes": 0, "subject": "<p>好的向老师 谢谢啦</p>", "created": "2018-04-04T02:25:17Z", "bucket_order": 170, "bucket_name": "Week 4/1 - 4/7", "type": "followup", "tag_good": [], "uid": "j7f1tr6wJNH", "children": [{"anon": "no", "folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": null}, "subject": "<p>额&#xff0c;我是来围观的。。这个问题不是我提的啊&#xff0c;如果大家有疑问可以发表留言 大家一起讨论啊&#xff01; : )</p>", "created": "2018-04-04T08:47:43Z", "bucket_order": 170, "bucket_name": "Week 4/1 - 4/7", "type": "feedback", "tag_good": [], "uid": "j7f1tr6wJNH", "children": [], "tag_good_arr": [], "id": "jfkunjswbg760y", "updated": "2018-04-04T08:47:43Z", "config": {}}], "tag_good_arr": [], "no_answer": 0, "id": "jfkgzqdqf2h530", "updated": "2018-04-04T02:25:17Z", "config": {}}], "tag_good_arr": [], "id": "jfkffypwx375ru", "config": {}, "status": "active", "drafts": null, "request_instructor": 0, "request_instructor_me": false, "bookmarked": 2, "num_favorites": 3, "my_favorite": false, "is_bookmarked": false, "is_tag_good": false, "q_edits": [], "i_edits": [], "s_edits": [], "t": 1643169356336, "default_anonymity": "no"}, "error": null, "aid": "kyv0lxrkfhs3la"}